dct_description_sm: This polygon shapefile represents the 1953 County Boundaries for China. The layer includes population census data and was primarily based on the "Historical Administrative Maps of the People's Republic of China," published by China Map Press, and some other yearly administrative maps. See the documentation for more information and a list of the layer variables.
dct_publisher_sm: Beijing Hua tong ren shi chang xin xi you xian ze ren gong si
dct_title_s: 1953 County Boundaries of China with Population Census Data
